      "content": "Raising engagement at the cost of diversity creates a feedback loop that can severely limit the appeal and longevity of your feed. Implementing diversity-focused algorithms requires careful A/B testing to ensure you aren't unfairly penalizing specific user segments while achieving federation metrics. Prioritizing cross-demographic content is a strategic move, but it must be clearly communicated to users to maintain trust and encourage participation.",
