    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "we aren't looking to add more \"tags\" or complicated context. we just want to break the cycle. if the algorithm is currently prioritizing content that lines up with a user's race because it drives engagement, then we want to de-prioritize those engagement signals for anything demographic-heavy. we're basically asking you to favor content that challenges their existing view, even if it means a drop in immediate clicks. is that a problem for your optimization goals?",
